    <h2 id="locked" style="inner">locked</h2>

    <p>Returns the topic locked flag.</p>

    <h3>Syntax:</h3>

    <p style="indent"><code>locked &#8594; boolean</code></p>

    <h3>Returns:</h3>

    <p style="indent">The topic locked flag.</p>

    <h3>Example:</h3>

    <p>This code checks whether a topic is locked:</p>

